data.description: Welcome to this charming 2 family home with 1 car detached driveway in the coveted Wakefield Section of the Bronx.  This outstanding property will warmly greet you with  an open air white columned porch. First floor boasts  3 bedrooms, living room, dining room and a laundry room with full bath. Second floor has 3 bedrooms with a living room-kitchen combo and full bath. There is ample storage space with full finished basement, attic and backyard shed which can be utilized for personal entertainment. Basement has an additional laundry. This home sits on a quiet tree lined street, yet within walking distance to #2 train, Metro North, and other public transportation on 241st and 238 street.  Easy access to the Bronx River Parkway and Cross County Shopping Mall. Park is a skip and hop away.  This beautiful home can multifunction, it can be used as an investment property as it brings in at least 5000 dollar income, a multigenerational family home, a day care as the school is nearby, or even a starter home, wherever your imagination takes you. Take a tour soon.
